====Pokémon Ruby-Sapphire====
{{main|Sapphire (Ruby-Sapphire)}}
A different counterpart to May, also called Sapphire, appears in [[Pokémon Ruby-Sapphire]]. Just like {{an|May|May's animated series counterpart}}, she is a {{pkmn|Coordinator}} who chooses {{p|Torchic}} as her [[first partner Pokémon]].
